# 2. Critical structural issues (must fix)

## 2.1 Duplicate / conflicting modules

### Problem

* “Aliases” appears more than once
* Git and SSH both try to handle key generation
* Clipboard + mount + aliases overlap responsibilities

### Fix

Define **single ownership per concern**:

| Concern         | Owner Module          |
| --------------- | --------------------- |
| SSH keys        | SSH module            |
| Git identity    | Git module            |
| Aliases         | Global Aliases module |
| Mount paths     | iOS Mount module      |
| Clipboard logic | Clipboard module      |

